I’m taking my pants off!!!

I’m getting #pantsdrunkforcancer and I want @rickiefowler @genobonnalie and @max.homa along with all my followers to join me and @longdrink in a Finnish tradition to help raise money for cancer research. 

For every qualifying post made between now and June 30th, The Long Drink will donate $10 to our Dahmen Family Foundation which directly supports testicular cancer research and early detection services. 

Here’s how you can help participate in the Finnish tradition of drinking at home in your underwear while supporting an important cause: 
- Take and post a #pantsdrunk photo with Long Drink
- tag @longdrink and #pantsdrunkforcancer
- invite and tag 3-5 friends to participate

Or you can always visit pantsdrunkforcancer.com and make a direct donation that Long Drink will match during the month of June.

No pants? No problem. For the entire month of June, we’re coming together to raise money for testicular cancer research while simultaneously partaking in the Finnish tradition of enjoying a drink in your favorite pair of underpants (also known as Kalsarikännit or pantsdrunk). For every #pantsdrunkforcancer post (stories or in-feed) @longdrink will donate $10 to the Dahmen Family Foundation which directly impacts cancer research, early detection services and patient support.

Wanna help? All you have to do is:
1) Post a photo enjoying Long Drink in your favorite pair of underpants
2) Tag @longdrink and use #pantsdrunkforcancer
3) Challenge your buddies to do the same

That’s it. Cheers!

Special moment being able to give back to what made me who I am. 
The Joel Dahmen Invitational is a thing 🤯. 

Thanks to the @wjga1976 and all the people that have helped launch our Dahmen Family Foundation, for reasons just like this. Excited about the future of these kids, and this foundation. 

#GiveBack #GiveBig

This month, we participated in the Finnish tradition of taking your pants of and enjoying a cold one, all in the name of cancer research. But June isn’t over yet! Now, through the end of the month, @longdrink will donate $5 to the Dahmen Family Foundation for every person that shares this post to their stories and tags @joeldahmen, @longdrink and uses #pantsdrunkforcancer. Yup, it’s that easy to join in and support a great cause! 

Want to up the ante? Long Drink will donate $10 for every person that posts a photo of themselves enjoying a Long Drink in their favorite pair of underpants. Don’t forget to tag @joeldahmen, @longdrink, and use #pantsdrunkforcancer. Cheers!

This #GivingTuesday our Family foundation was proud to give away $10,000 to Arizona Cancer Foundation for Children and help those families in need. 

If you are looking for a great place to give, please consider our foundation so we can keep doing this across the country through the game of golf. We want to help children and families going through cancer to better their communities and life around them. It is why I play the game, and try to keep life fun.

#GivingTuesday #ThankYou #maybeGenoWillMatch
